Class ListUrlPattern

java.lang.Object
  org.middleheaven.process.web.UrlPattern
      org.middleheaven.process.web.ListUrlPattern

public class ListUrlPattern
extends UrlPattern

A composition of UrlPatterns. The matching accours in the order of insertion of the individual UrlPattern objects. if the matchAll flag is ative all the patterns must match the input in some degreed. If the matchAll flag is not ative, the maximum of the match will be returned.
